{
  "stem": "21354.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we made sure that we did our job well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after a while, again, they asked for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't tell us what for, but I was always anxious, young, to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I put my name forwards, and I thought we were going to go to Crete, on airborne landings to Crete.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No such luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No such luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some weeks afterwards, my name was called on parade, and I was informed that I had been singled out for special duties.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What the special duties, they didn't know and I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was sent to Cowes-- not to Cowes, to London at first, and I was informed that they had learned of my qualifications that I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they wanted to use me for special duties.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I was seconded to the special section of the intelligent that dealt with information on Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had code and cipher listening devices, everything possible to assist our air force in information.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or airborne, to sit in an aircraft, to fly over, all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did my tests very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I became a sergeant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From then onwards, of course, I enjoyed the life in the sergeants' mess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we're now into '33--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43, '43, forgive me. '43.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Became a sergeant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started in Kingston and Beachy Head-- that's the highest point Eastbourne-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [? all ?] [INAUDIBLE] stationed, then we were going on to the end of '43, early '44.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, they wanted special duty volunteers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a sergeant, and I joined the Combined Operations, which are well-known as the Number 4 Commandos for the Royal Air Force.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our duty was to prepare for D-Day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know when D-Day was to be, but we knew a landing was imminent.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
